10 An Act relating to public finance; enacting the
Strategic Bitcoin Reserve Act; providing definitions;
11 permitting certain investments by the State
Treasurer; limiting investments; directing certain
12 taxes and fees be paid to the State General Fund;
permitting investment of state retirement funds;
13 providing for codification; and providing an
effective date.
